keyValuePair.Value: Have you missed out now?
The %1s season's almost over. You lost your way badly in the chase for promotion. Do you think your boys are out of it now?
We won't give up yet.
I've told the boys what I expect from them. We have to go into every game and look to win. Let's have no regrets. Who knows what could still happen?

We'll concentrate on ourselves.
We can't affect what happens to the teams around us. We have to concentrate on our own performances. If we're winning, we'll still have a chance.
Maybe the lads have blown it.
I'm not sure how the boys are feeling. Do they think it's over? Well, I don't. I've told them to go out and finish strong. If nothing else, we owe that much to the fans.
Do you think you can beat the drop?
